<D>__{perceval, you have returned!}
<C>__{arthur}
<D>__{ready my knights for battle; they will ride with their king once more. i have lived through others far too long! lancelot carried my honor and guenevere my guilt. my knights have fought my causes. mordred carries my sins. now, at last, i will rule.}
